{"tid":347704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人分享一件見工搞笑事/難忘事","createTime":"2017-08-05T05:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T11:43:34.000Z","uid":65563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de51a243d0502ad45302965e688abc9b332718f2","tid":347704,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"話說15,16歲時候，同2個fd一齊去見暑期工，咁份工係做市場調查既公司黎(唔係sale野，係正經問下人問卷嗰啲)，主要問下香港人飲食習慣。<br />\n<br />\n我仲好記得當時係喺北角某商業大廈見工，咁我地都怕係伏就門口望望先，但望落又似係正正常常既公司，而且人都既然到左，咁就入去啦。<br />\n一入到去填完表，就叫我地入房等做interview ，點知原來係成30幾人既group interview ，咁我地3個就專登分開坐，費事好似黎玩咁。<br />\n<br />\n之後個HR入黎，就叫我地每個人自己介紹自己，同埋點解想做呢份工。身為一個毒絲，一路都好摺，唔慣對住咁多人，再加上第一次見工就係30幾人既group interview ...我個腦好空白咁簡單介紹完自己後，我就答...因為我想幫問卷搵答案，所以黎見工。<br />\n<br />\n然後....我只記得我答完，先知自己語無倫次，紅都面哂，全場既人包括HR都呆左幾秒同忍笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nInterview完左後，一出門口，我2個朋友瘋狂爆笑，笑到流哂眼水，而我仍然面紅同呆滯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過每次諗返起，都覺得幾好笑...點解當時自己會答埋d咁既野。"},{"pid":"3946ff6f31cb44fb91c6fabe3033944f90f1ac33","tid":347704,"uid":72445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:07:24.000Z","msg":"最後有冇請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff5e898938b08d309f62960bfa4efe8c6c53c05","tid":347704,"uid":80918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:09:13.000Z","msg":"重點 你個時講咗啲咩都冇講。。。分享唔到你既喜悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf18a93b5b094e3c1b72c6a526b542465632c94","tid":347704,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後有冇請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後無請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗個HR都唔夠膽請我"},{"pid":"062e4d5697800d9e82769fc0f35149dafdcd7615","tid":347704,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重點 你個時講咗啲咩都冇講。。。分享唔到你既喜悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我嗰時淨係簡單介紹完自己，答左要幫問卷搵答案後，我就已經成個人緊張又震哂，然後咩都講唔出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbac91af6d508b4b997697c1943bfa108fc085b","tid":347704,"uid":49524,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n<br />\n個次見份暑期工 個濕鳩老細in我<br />\n佢其中有一條問題係問我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你覺得打一份工有咩準則？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「其實份份工都唔同嘅...」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話音未落 佢就即刻搏咀<br />\n「唔好講份份工都唔同 講下你以前返嘅工」<br />\n<br />\n我呆左一呆 之後就逐份工數俾佢聽啦<br />\n我數第一份工未講完 佢就話「錯」<br />\n好 數第二份工 佢又話「錯」<br />\n已經燥燥地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 野都唔俾人講埋先<br />\n數第三份工 「錯」<br />\n<br />\n我深吸左啖氣 忍住道氣問佢「咁不如你指教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做野經驗唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n佢第一句就答我<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「其實份份工都唔同嘅」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbecd3a91b6f493930d073eb5d1a7831856db256","tid":347704,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n<br />\n個次見份暑期工 個濕鳩老細in我<br />\n佢其中有一條問題係問我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你覺得打一份工有咩準則？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">