oji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nInterview完左後，一出門口，我2個朋友瘋狂爆笑，笑到流哂眼水，而我仍然面紅同呆滯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過每次諗返起，都覺得幾好笑...點解當時自己會答埋d咁既野。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家諗返起都覺得自己好癲，點解會答埋啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2433acf2e570ba892a7863534130c4f1f1c59159","tid":347704,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要做呢份工<br />\n我試過答因爲無錢所以要搵錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n答得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有邊個見工唔係為左要份工，要揾錢。"},{"pid":"8e47399fd1cde42b0482900305072785bf629716","tid":347704,"uid":60028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"前排見工，兩女一男<br />\n<br />\n男：平時有咩興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：踢波+睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男：咁撐開邊隊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後個男即刻黑面兼冇再追問落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但最後請左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb3d00fc221fa39664fbdb767098801bc295229","tid":347704,"uid":65563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排見工，兩女一男<br />\n<br />\n男：平時有咩興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：踢波+睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男：咁撐開邊隊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後個男即刻黑面兼冇再追問落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但最後請左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHaha...咁返工之後有無同佢傾波經，打下友誼波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}